metadata.name: STPE #1
metadata.description: Hello, I am an STPE ambassador from LEN Meta Corp, and your guide to the ever expanding Legioverse! The Legioverse is a digital universe that connects the many varied and expansive metaverses together through community, commerce, and cross-verse interoperability. There are many kinds of ambassadors, and each of us has unique traits and access to special abilities tied to a specific Metaverse connected through the Legioverse. Through your interactions with me, you gain access to our operations inside the STEPN ecosystem. This allows you to stake this NFT to earn, vote, and trade on our digital commodities exchange. Some of our ambassadors also grant access to special perks within the Legioverse that will not be accessible any other way, but will only be able too once at least 2000 ambassadors have been assigned, and we can reveal our true look! We look forward to meeting you!
